Package: cnefetools
Title: Tools for Working with Brazilian CNEFE 2022 Address Data
Version: 0.0.1.9002
Authors@R: 
    person("Jorge Ubirajara", "Pedreira Junior",
           email = "jorge.ubirajara@ufba.br",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides helper functions to work with the Cadastro Nacional de 
    Endereços para Fins Estatísticos (CNEFE) from the 2022 Brazilian census. 
    The initial version focuses on efficiently downloading, caching, and 
    reading municipality-level CNEFE CSV files into Arrow tables for 
    downstream analysis.
